{"id": "ChIJK8WHcqbHwoARsma5QbETv_E", "rating": 4.1, "userRatingCount": 130, "displayName": {"text": "Gentle Monster Los Angeles", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJK8WHcqbHwoARsma5QbETv_E/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25Cek5HMW1kVEF5WkVkd05qSjNOV1JwTUZWSGJIYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Gentle Monster makes a strong first impression with a large sculptural installation at the entrance that reminds me of a StarCraft Dragoon. Inside, there are moving art pieces that give the space a modern, gallery-like atmosphere — it feels more like an art exhibition than a typical eyewear store.\n\nThe frames are stylish and well-displayed, and I was able to try on a variety of options. The staff were very friendly and helpful, offering clear explanations throughout the process.\n\nMost frames are priced in the $250–$350 range. Single-vision lenses can be added as an extra service, but progressive lenses are not available, which is something to keep in mind.\n\nI walked from my nearby office, but if you’re visiting, you’ll likely need to find street parking or a paid parking lot nearby, which may add to the overall cost.\n\nOverall, a unique and visually impressive eyewear shopping experience in DTLA.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Gentle Monster makes a strong first impression with a large sculptural installation at the entrance that reminds me of a StarCraft Dragoon. Inside, there are moving art pieces that give the space a modern, gallery-like atmosphere — it feels more like an art exhibition than a typical eyewear store.\n\nThe frames are stylish and well-displayed, and I was able to try on a variety of options. The staff were very friendly and helpful, offering clear explanations throughout the process.\n\nMost frames are priced in the $250–$350 range. Single-vision lenses can be added as an extra service, but progressive lenses are not available, which is something to keep in mind.\n\nI walked from my nearby office, but if you’re visiting, you’ll likely need to find street parking or a paid parking lot nearby, which may add to the overall cost.\n\nOverall, a unique and visually impressive eyewear shopping experience in DTLA.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Ahacool Kim", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/107771775586078041551/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWII91BLScs7M7RWArxVYsddhX6V7Zx9ukobFEyPWUquvz9JLjy=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-30T05:26:35.650638507Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25Cek5HMW1kVEF5WkVkd05qSjNOV1JwTUZWSGJIYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25Cek5HMW1kVEF5WkVkd05qSjNOV1JwTUZWSGJIYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c7a67287c52b:0xf1bf13b141b966b2"}, {"name": "places/ChIJK8WHcqbHwoARsma5QbETv_E/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21wQmExbHBZMlI1YWxRM1pHTnBiRVV6YXpCaFJtYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Abigail is like the sun and the moon and the stars all wrapped up in one! She’s got the most radiant & disarming presence, I am so lucky to have come in on a day she was working!\n\nI’m about to travel overseas for a bit and I wanted to bring this pair of half-frame Gentle Monster glasses that I had worn every day until a lens popped out. I don’t wear prescription glasses, so I didn’t technically neeeeeeeed them but Abigail was able to squeeze me in for an adjustment before my leave for Ireland, so I would be looking quite distinguished at the airport.\n\nI showed up really late to my appointment (bad practice) and she still adjusted my glasses even after I walked through those double doors thirty minutes late. And oh so quickly, at that! It was seriously such a gift to have such an engaging, capable, & gentle person across from me at the desk. Makes me want to support Gentle Monster and its wonderful team all the more! Thank you, Abigail!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Abigail is like the sun and the moon and the stars all wrapped up in one! She’s got the most radiant & disarming presence, I am so lucky to have come in on a day she was working!\n\nI’m about to travel overseas for a bit and I wanted to bring this pair of half-frame Gentle Monster glasses that I had worn every day until a lens popped out. I don’t wear prescription glasses, so I didn’t technically neeeeeeeed them but Abigail was able to squeeze me in for an adjustment before my leave for Ireland, so I would be looking quite distinguished at the airport.\n\nI showed up really late to my appointment (bad practice) and she still adjusted my glasses even after I walked through those double doors thirty minutes late. And oh so quickly, at that! It was seriously such a gift to have such an engaging, capable, & gentle person across from me at the desk. Makes me want to support Gentle Monster and its wonderful team all the more! Thank you, Abigail!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Janssen Van De Yacht", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/114926010747856854457/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWfPk6EYJeu6Z3k6gKGBIW6gFLcVexQmT0U_QkC5NDj5LzxaeHtlQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-04T19:52:48.627763833Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21wQmExbHBZMlI1YWxRM1pHTnBiRVV6YXpCaFJtYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21wQmExbHBZMlI1YWxRM1pHTnBiRVV6YXpCaFJtYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c7a67287c52b:0xf1bf13b141b966b2"}, {"name": "places/ChIJK8WHcqbHwoARsma5QbETv_E/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tKZlVUaHVVMFpxVGxwd2RUWnBkbXRXTWtKRk4yYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "5 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "I had bought a Gentle Monster sunglass 2 years ago and was impressed on how sturdy and high quality the product is. I went to check out the showroom in person with the intention of maybe buying one more. And behold, I came out with not one but three.  I knew it was going to be scary for my wallet but it was well worth it. There are a lot of variety of frames and len colors. Every showroom staff were friendly. I do want to make a major shout out to 2 particular humans in there.\nJimmy!\nGenesis!\nThey were both incredible very patient and kind in helping me choose my sun glasses. I was able to try them on and they helped me compare and discuss which specs complimented my facial shape or enhanced my tone. I never felt rushed. I am happy with my purchase and I look foward to rocking all my Gentle Monster specs.  With kindness and warm regards, thank you Gentle Monster LA.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I had bought a Gentle Monster sunglass 2 years ago and was impressed on how sturdy and high quality the product is. I went to check out the showroom in person with the intention of maybe buying one more. And behold, I came out with not one but three.  I knew it was going to be scary for my wallet but it was well worth it. There are a lot of variety of frames and len colors. Every showroom staff were friendly. I do want to make a major shout out to 2 particular humans in there.\nJimmy!\nGenesis!\nThey were both incredible very patient and kind in helping me choose my sun glasses. I was able to try them on and they helped me compare and discuss which specs complimented my facial shape or enhanced my tone. I never felt rushed. I am happy with my purchase and I look foward to rocking all my Gentle Monster specs.  With kindness and warm regards, thank you Gentle Monster LA.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Hoy", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/118233081972396663966/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUa566D6iLg9ChBxrTB4ghSKFaftrq4_h6g0YUkzsVOZb7uXAQa=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-01-25T21:02:49.988657093Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tKZlVUaHVVMFpxVGxwd2RUWnBkbXRXTWtKRk4yYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tKZlVUaHVVMFpxVGxwd2RUWnBkbXRXTWtKRk4yYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c7a67287c52b:0xf1bf13b141b966b2"}, {"name": "places/ChIJK8WHcqbHwoARsma5QbETv_E/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25NeVlYRXlVVmwxZEVkb1pIRTBaM2wyU21aUkxYYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Great experience today! Way better than shopping online. Walking through the store feels like walking an art gallery. The staff was friendly and helpful, like Jimmy, Zoe and Abigail. They helped me try on many different styles of glasses, and even helped me see what was new and trended.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Great experience today! Way better than shopping online. Walking through the store feels like walking an art gallery. The staff was friendly and helpful, like Jimmy, Zoe and Abigail. They helped me try on many different styles of glasses, and even helped me see what was new and trended.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Noah", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111703495662315990129/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX9aFNBuC3_THIIhn_LCXpiSZXPZP77Jr2EwgKSC-yDgtfyeos=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-10T03:13:58.073320914Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25NeVlYRXlVVmwxZEVkb1pIRTBaM2wyU21aUkxYYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25NeVlYRXlVVmwxZEVkb1pIRTBaM2wyU21aUkxYYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c7a67287c52b:0xf1bf13b141b966b2"}, {"name": "places/ChIJK8WHcqbHwoARsma5QbETv_E/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21Jd2RsZE9RMmxFZEdoWWFscHBjek5VWlUxQlZXYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Super friendly staff and an amazing store design. The artwork alone makes it worth visiting! feels more like an art exhibit than a retail space which made the visit all the more worth it :)", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Super friendly staff and an amazing store design. The artwork alone makes it worth visiting! feels more like an art exhibit than a retail space which made the visit all the more worth it :)", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Soogyum Kim", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/101036260761035072864/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXIR_-KplKHPUfjhbUTUZIbPH4RpHjtR4ThzPINCCfOmpxA7XM=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-11T21:23:24.655906787Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21Jd2RsZE9RMmxFZEdoWWFscHBjek5VWlUxQlZXYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21Jd2RsZE9RMmxFZEdoWWFscHBjek5VWlUxQlZXYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c7a67287c52b:0xf1bf13b141b966b2"}], "photos": [{"name": "places/ChIJK8WHcqbHwoARsma5QbETv_E/photos/AWCwydiEPH6pCc9dncZ2OAboxbpbC_G7hfFTi04l31oUaE1pEpaTAOthB8ecZC6yQyv3DYTxibZIz9MgTqtqAwr0lQ0wGxtotThH52hV_m2V77JNj1FMDq1cTbPwcIGVXzMR7qIOGK36tOLWTibtqz_I5XmpWIVp-cEP4TVpelX8uU4U3AZQLOgDxzSQQM0JVd50X_pmrHj6F5whJZHw0ZktAXR3CBUFXQXcG7lo-x0Ahdxwv18H_2xS722qV1YLoqE5M46VDnxnQNhYZe_LyI3vPYwqyzk91zHyM8fvqoM1E4yztVF64AMv-0N62SeoaP5edI6tIX8npO1TrNo4KhBUT7DnyMzQoCOrdndSk5aovidM6ARHG7j1E56JkP_4BM3mQw_0KdBVzrHXP2n8wi3fVT0GsYOwfBqLdc9vzCPQ5I9NdRif", "widthPx": 3024, "heightPx": 4032, "authorAttributions": [{"displayName": "Eli Kim", "uri": "https://maps.google.com/ma